    <Folder>
      <name>Atkins (260)</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>260</name>
        <description>&lt;b&gt;Atkins (260)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;2024 — Gulf of Alaska&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;4 passes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 1&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 1): North to south of A site&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 2&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 1): Right of Pass 1; started photo pass earlier&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 3&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 1): B site; disturbed 15; perpendicular to Passes 1 and 2&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 4&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 1): Same as Pass 3 but started photo pass earlier; count animals in the water; disturbed 5 more; animals at end of this pass overlap with A site</description>
