    <Folder>
      <name>Marmot (212)</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>212</name>
        <description>&lt;b&gt;Marmot (212)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;2024 — Gulf of Alaska&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;5 passes&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 1&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 2): South to north; Beach 7 (A site) through Beach 5&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 2&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 3): Beach 4 (B site); pretty sure we got straggler males at beginning but drifted off rookery&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 3&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 3): Left of Pass 2; Beach 5 may be in photos at start of pass&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 4&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 3): Same as Pass 3; definitely got rookery this pass; check for 4 on left at start (straggler males group)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pass 5&lt;/b&gt; (Jul 3)</description>
